# Environment Variables Template
# Add these in Cloudflare Pages Dashboard: Settings > Environment variables > Production

# ============================================
# Google Sheets Integration (REQUIRED)
# ============================================
# STEP 1: Create a Google Sheet
# - Go to https://sheets.google.com
# - Create a new spreadsheet
# - Add headers in row 1: Timestamp | Name | Email | Phone | Company | Total Annual Impact | Selected Pain Points | Pain Point Details | Raw Inputs
# - Copy the spreadsheet ID from the URL (it's the long string between /d/ and /edit)
#   Example URL: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ABC123xyz/edit
#   Spreadsheet ID: 1ABC123xyz

# STEP 2: Get Google Sheets API Key
# - Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# - Create a new project (or select existing)
# - Enable Google Sheets API: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/sheets.googleapis.com
# - Create credentials > API Key
# - Copy the API key

# STEP 3: Make your spreadsheet public (read/write for anyone with link)
# - In your Google Sheet, click "Share" button
# - Change access to "Anyone with the link" > "Editor"
# - This allows the API to write data without OAuth

GOOGLE_SHEETS_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
GOOGLE_SHEETS_SPREADSHEET_ID=your_spreadsheet_id_here

